Various plugins (eg. Perforce, Subversion) reply on issue key matching. By default, JIRA ignores keys that are part of URLs. This is a problem with svn/p4 plugins (see the [p4 bug|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/PERF-62], [svn bug|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/SVN-37]), where people frequently do enter the URL instead of the key.

